   A. User Access\
       By design, all users who are added to your network (create in wp-admin/network/user-new.php) will \
       have subscriber access to all sites on your network. User created in individual subdomain dashboard\
       have access to that subdomain only. You can use a plugin, such as {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/multisite-user-management"}}{\fldrslt Multisite User Management}} to \
       manage user network roles.\
       To add new plugin go to:  /wp-admin/network/plugin-install.php\
